"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Oil prices have dropped after Iran announced that a key waterway is open for commercial ships during the ceasefire. This caused Brent crude prices to fall by ten percent.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oil Prices Drop\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los precios del petr\u00f3leo bajaron despu\u00e9s de que Ir\u00e1n anunci\u00f3 que un canal importante est\u00e1 abierto para barcos comerciales durante la tregua. Esto hizo que los precios del crudo Brent bajaran un diez por ciento.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Precios del Petr\u00f3leo Bajan\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president has stated on social media that Israel is not allowed to bomb Lebanon. The ceasefire is being celebrated in Lebanon, but it might be hard to keep it going.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on Israel and Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dijo en redes sociales que Israel no puede bombardear L\u00edbano. La tregua se celebra en L\u00edbano, pero puede ser dif\u00edcil mantenerla.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre Israel y L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kinahan, who is in his 40s, was arrested in Dubai because of an arrest warrant from the Irish courts.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kinahan Arrested\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kinahan, que tiene unos 40 a\u00f1os, fue arrestado en Dub\u00e1i por una orden de arresto de los tribunales irlandeses.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Kinahan Arrestado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The UK government has stopped a rapper from entering the country because of his past pro-Nazi and racist statements.\",            \"english_title\": \"Rapper Banned from UK\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno del Reino Unido no dej\u00f3 entrar a un rapero al pa\u00eds por sus declaraciones pro-nazis y racistas del pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rapero Prohibido en Reino Unido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Pope Leo XIV is visiting Cameroon and will go to Angola on Saturday.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope Visits Africa\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa Leo XIV est\u00e1 visitando Camer\u00fan y ir\u00e1 a Angola el s\u00e1bado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papa Visita \u00c1frica\"        }    ]}"